# Technology Stack Documentation

This document outlines the primary technologies and tools used in this project. **It is important to keep this document updated with any changes to the technology stack.**

## Frontend

- **Framework:** [React](mdc:package.json) (with [Vite](mdc:vite.config.ts))
- **UI Components:**
    - [Radix UI](mdc:package.json) (unstyled, accessible component primitives)
    - [Shadcn UI](mdc:components.json) (built on Radix UI with Tailwind styling)
    - Icons: [Lucide React](mdc:package.json)
- **Styling:** [Tailwind CSS](mdc:tailwind.config.ts)
- **Routing:** [React Router DOM](mdc:package.json)
- **State Management:**
    - [Zustand](mdc:package.json) (global state) - See [src/stores/](mdc:src/stores)
    - [React Context API](mdc:src/contexts) (component-level state)
- **Rich Text Editors:**
    - [BlockNote](mdc:package.json)
    - [Lexical](mdc:package.json)
- **Canvas/Drawing:** [Excalidraw](mdc:public/excalidraw-assets)
- **UI Utilities:**
    - Drag and Drop: [@dnd-kit](mdc:package.json)
    - Forms: [react-hook-form](mdc:package.json) with [zod](mdc:package.json) validation
    - Dates: [date-fns](mdc:package.json)
    - Charts: [Recharts](mdc:package.json)
    - Animation: [Framer Motion](mdc:package.json)
    - Notifications: [sonner](mdc:package.json)
    - HTML to Images: [html2canvas](mdc:package.json)
    - Chinese Language: [pinyin-pro](mdc:package.json)
    - IDs: [uuid](mdc:package.json)

## Backend

- **Cloud Platform:** [Supabase](mdc:.cursor/rules/backend_structure.mdc)
    - **Database:** PostgreSQL
    - **Authentication:** Supabase Auth
    - **Storage:** Supabase Storage
    - **Serverless Functions:** TypeScript-based [Edge Functions](mdc:supabase/functions)
- **API Client:** [Axios](mdc:package.json)

## Build & Tooling

- **Package Manager:** [Bun](mdc:bun.lockb)
- **Build Tool:** [Vite](mdc:vite.config.ts)
- **Language:** [TypeScript](mdc:tsconfig.json)
- **Linting:** [ESLint](mdc:eslint.config.js)

## Deployment & Hosting

- **Platform:** [Vercel](mdc:vercel.json)

## Version Control

- **System:** Git
- **Hosting:** GitHub

**Note:** When adding new technologies or libraries to the project, please update this document accordingly to maintain an accurate overview of the technology stack.
